txt: 上海文通大学
SHANGHAI JIAO TONG UNIVERSITY
EfficientTDNN: Efficient Architecture Search for
Speaker Recognition in the Wild
Speaker：王瑞，同济大学
Venue:Room412.SEIEE-3
Host: Prof. Kai Yu
Abstract:
Rui Wang is curently pursuing the Ph.D. degree in computer science and technology from Tongji University
He received B.S. and M.S. degrees in mechanical design manufacture and automation and measurement technol-
ogy and instruments fom Zhejiang Sci-Tech University, respectively. His curent research interests focus on au
tomatic speaker recognition systems and neural architecture search.
This tallk presents a novel neural architecture search method for speaker recognition, called EfficientTDNN
The proposed EfficientTDNN aims to design efficient architectures that reduce storage and computation con-
straints while maintaining recognition accuracy. A novel search space borrowed from time-delay neural networks
is developed in EfficientTDNN and supports model scaling in network depth, kemel size, and layer width. Effi-
cientTDNN provides a practical solution for deploying speech processing applications on edge devices.
The manuscript has been submitted to IEEE Transactions on Infomations Forensics and Security on 20th,
April, 2021. Access to the report at arXiv. Feel free for questions.
Bio:
王瑞，目前在同济大学攻读计算机科学与技术学科的博士学位。他从浙江理工大学的机械设计制
造及其自动化专业和测试计量技术及仪器取得学士学位与硕土学位。他目前的研究方向是自动说话人
识别系统、神经网络结构搜索。
此次报告分享说话人识别任务上的神经网路结构搜索技术EfficientTDNN。该方法旨在设计高效的
网络结构，在确保识别准确率的前提下降低模型所需的资源约束。它设计了一种以时延神经网络为基
础的搜索空间，支持网络结构在网络深度、卷积核大小和网络宽度上的尺寸缩放。EfficientTDNN提供
十种面向语音处理的自动化网络结构搜索方案
为智能语音服务在边缘设备的部署提供了有效的解
决方案
报告的论文稿件已提交到IEEETransactionsonInformationsForensicsandSecurity(2021.04.20)）
已在arXiv公开。
期待大家的专业建设与看法
